strings: <voice_0x01001905><se_def>Dhoulmagus: It is an honour to be allowed to entertain you, Your Majesty. I have prepared some...tricks for your amusement.
<voice_0x01001907><se_low>King Trode: Most impressive! Yes, most impressive indeed. You will stay here at the castle tonight. I insist! As a reward for that remarkable show.
<voice_0x01001908><se_def>Dhoulmagus: A-ha-ha... You are too kind, Your Majesty.
